title: Airbnb Price Prediction
description: Designed regression models to predict NYC Airbnb listing prices using structured data, surpassing baseline RMSE benchmarks. Final RMSE - 90.36.

title: Diabetes Prediction Model
description: Built a binary classification model using Random Forest and XGBoost to predict diabetes risk based on 17 medical and demographic features from a dataset of 9,500+ patient records.

title: Data Analysis of US Power Outages
description: Analyzed major U.S. power outages using Python, uncovering trends, correlations, and regional differences in outage durations.

title: College Selection Tool
description: Developed a college selection tool in Excel to help international students find suitable undergraduate programs

title: Stock Market Analysis
description: Analyzed trends in the stock market
